data.title: Custom Plastics Manufacturing - CV Plastics
data.meta_description: CV Plastics provides high-quality grease traps, trade waste solutions & custom plastics. Get fast quotes, precise fabrication & nationwide delivery. We cater to various industries & offer personalized service. Call now for a quote.
data.text:
We make it easy for you to do business with us.

Simply reach out, receive a quick quote, and enjoy the benefits of our highly skilled fabricators and machinists, with fast turnaround and reliable delivery.

Our confident, knowledgeable, and friendly team is ready to assist you every step of the way

Reach out to our friendly team to discuss your requirements and get all the information you need.

We’re here to provide knowledgeable assistance and answer any questions you may have.

For grease traps, trade waste, custom water tanks or custom plastic fabrication or machining, we’re here to help.

For pricing or more information call us on 03 5442 8728.
